    "description": "Power Pushout 是一款回合制策略游戏，在史诗般的亚洲环境中加入了武术元素。选择您的战士和大师角色，并与他们在一场狂野的战斗中争夺棋盘的控制权。要么你把你的对手从棋盘上扔掉，要么你征服对方的塔来赢得胜利。但要小心，你的敌人不会像忍者一样偷偷溜过你的部队并篡夺胜利。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>用酷炫的终结技打败你的对手。<br>剑术和功夫踢都在议事日程上。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/c323382ab83243c4d93156ebc9122a54.poster.avif?t=1641503168\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/c323382ab83243c4d93156ebc9122a54.webm?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/c323382ab83243c4d93156ebc9122a54.mp4?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>选择你的战士和大师人物，并结合他们的力量点来摧毁你对手的人物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/d06b3f8fca8e389778c0a25c07575cc9.poster.avif?t=1641503168\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/d06b3f8fca8e389778c0a25c07575cc9.webm?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/d06b3f8fca8e389778c0a25c07575cc9.mp4?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>使用地图编辑器创建您自己的禅宗战争花园。<br>智能放置系统可帮助您快速取得成果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/fe9c7d9f96eb4d1401bf66c07f9d8c16.poster.avif?t=1641503168\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/fe9c7d9f96eb4d1401bf66c07f9d8c16.webm?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/fe9c7d9f96eb4d1401bf66c07f9d8c16.mp4?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>你可以触发地震或添加超级水晶来让你的对手大吃一惊。<br>超级水晶为您的角色提供额外的力量或更大的运动范围。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/0fbeef9bf181a29c3cbd3753139f9c39.poster.avif?t=1641503168\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/0fbeef9bf181a29c3cbd3753139f9c39.webm?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773990/extras/0fbeef9bf181a29c3cbd3753139f9c39.mp4?t=1641503168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Power Pushout 为您提供 4 种不同的游戏模式：<br><strong>经典</strong>、<strong>普通</strong>、<strong>破坏</strong> 和 <strong>足球</strong>。<br>每种模式都可以在线或本地与朋友或基于机器学习和智能启发式的 AI 一起玩。</li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 简体中文, 丹麦语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 日语, 韩语, 荷兰语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 瑞典语, 泰语, 捷克语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 匈牙利语, 越南语, 繁体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
